response.overview: Weekend 2 of the Coachella Valley Music and Arts Festival. Still, the band managed to get through about 20 songs and performed the entire 1978 "Bullet" EP in its entirety.  Here is everything The Original Misfits performed during Weekend 2.  "Death Comes Ripping” “I Turned Into A Martian” “20 Eyes” “Vampira” “Violent World”  “London Dungeon” “Mommy, Can I Go Out And Kill Tonight?” “Teenagers From Mars” “Children In Heat” “We Are 138” “Hollywood Babylon” “Bullet” “Some Kinda Hate” “Hybrid Moments” “Halloween” “Horror Business” “Skulls” “Astro Zombies” “Last Caress”
response.title: Misfits - Coachella Weekend 2
